message: Search intensifies for missing 15 yo Bonney Lake girl after man charged with sex trafficking.

data.description: TACOMA, Wash. -- A sex offender arrested during the weekend was charged Tuesday with kidnapping, raping and sex-trafficking a 15-year-old Bonney Lake girl who has been missing and the subject of an intense search for weeks. She is still missing. Christopher Russell Fitzpatrick, 39, appeared in Pierc...
data.title: Search intensifies for missing Bonney Lake girl after man charged with kidnapping, raping, trafficking her
